data.title: United States Lifesaving Association National Lifeguard and Junior Lifeguard Championships
data.meta_description: This event features individual and team events including swimming, running, board paddling, surfboat rowing and surf ski paddleing.  The event draws over 1,000 lifeguards, former lifeguards and junior lifeguards from around the nation.  The Sarcoma Alliance will have a tent every day of the event.  If you are interested in…
